<subSubSection pageId="87" pageNumber="145" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="87.[1382,2593,3119,3476]" pageId="87" pageNumber="145">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Desmarest" authorityYear="1822" box="[1384,1642,3163,3192]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="mariannus">Pteropus mariannus</taxonomicName>
is in the 
<taxonomicName box="[1773,1859,3163,3192]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Moraceae" genus="Pleropus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="griseus">griseus</taxonomicName>
species group. Taxa 
<taxonomicName authorityName="K. Andersen" authorityYear="1908" box="[2154,2283,3163,3192]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="pelewensis">pelewensis</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1883" box="[2302,2407,3163,3192]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="ualanus">ualanus</taxonomicName>
, and yapensis are often listed as subspecies but have been confirmed as separate from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Desmarest" authorityYear="1822" box="[2444,2585,3199,3232]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="mariannus">mariannus</taxonomicName>
. Taxonomic status of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1870" box="[1677,1848,3238,3271]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="loochoensis">P. loochoensis</taxonomicName>
by J. E. Gray in 1870 from 
<collectingRegion box="[2232,2355,3238,3271]" country="Japan" name="Okinawa" pageId="87" pageNumber="145">Okinawa</collectingRegion>
Islands (Ryukyu Islands, 
<collectingCountry box="[1495,1581,3277,3310]" name="Japan" pageId="87" pageNumber="145">Japan</collectingCountry>
) remains uncertain; it is known from just two specimens collected in the 19&quot; century, and it is here considered conspecific with or an extinct subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Desmarest" authorityYear="1822" box="[1383,1558,3355,3388]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="145" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="mariannus">P. mariannus</taxonomicName>
. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
